[Kiran Chandrasekher](https://www.linkedin.com/in/kiran-chandrasekher/?trk=opento_nprofile_details) has been arwarded a prestigious [Barry Goldwater Scholarship and Excellence in Education Foundation](https://goldwaterscholarship.gov/)!
Kiran is an undergraduate researcher that investigates with me the importance of seasonality and human movement on dengue dynamics. 
Congrats Kiran - so well deserved! 
